{"tid":1634062,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台工會：譴責傷及記者的暴力行為, 但亦質疑《禁蒙面法》","createTime":"2019-10-07T06:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T11:23:38.000Z","uid":134071,"like":87,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"3ed7d6be3a6fab3c614b2cafa4e667dd576ae3cd","tid":1634062,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:23:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484738-20191007.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484738-20191007.htm&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn4WZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=c74ba297\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484738-20191007.htm&h=cd7ab96f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484738-20191007.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n港台工會：嚴厲譴責任何傷及記者暴力行為<br />\n<br />\n香港電台節目製作人員工會就近日有本台同事採訪時受傷發表聲明，嚴厲譴責任何傷及記者的暴力行為，並對受傷同事致以慰問，重申任何傷害前線新聞工作者的行為，均嚴重干預新聞自由。<br />\n<br />\n工會表示，昨日在警方於灣仔清場期間，本台電視部一名記者採訪時被燃燒彈誤中，頭盔及雨衣着火，面部灼傷，須送院治理。聲明又提到本月一日，本台英文新聞部一名記者在長沙灣採訪時，右眼角疑中彈受傷，即時紅腫，一度差點未能張開右眼，同日，一名本台攝影師在太子採訪時，腳部疑中彈受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>工會又質疑政府未有汲取修例爭議教訓，沒充份諮詢就試圖繞過立法會，推出禁蒙面法，並新增刑事罪行，令衝突有可能進一步升溫。工會促請政府勿火上加油，認真回應社會訴求，徹底解決問題。 </strong>"},{"pid":"df75adc9f29b3520acef3c453cdb53ac907ab92f","tid":1634062,"uid":134071,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:23:45.000Z","msg":"真係幫到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nRTHK證實: 本台記者著火, 黑衣示威者即時幫忙救人<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1630128/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1630128/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c6ae4b5a774bfa472bdb0a37a015751e0c990972","tid":1634062,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s