0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JG49P0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJG49P0v.jpg&h=bfdca82e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行動Post : <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634329\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634329</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">目標一、哂馬</span></strong></span><br />\n由於警狗唔再批不反，即使批左亦會製造衝突。<br />\n為左令和理非可以舒舒服服地出返黎，展示人數同民意，<br />\n所以就利用黃店門外既人龍，製造畫面同話題吸引媒體注意。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">目標二、支持黃色經濟</span></span></strong><br />\n依幾個月生意難免受影響，加上可能被藍絲杯葛，<br />\n良心黃店係好需要大家支持。<br />\n最實際既支持當然就係拎銀包出黎，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>入錢入錢入錢！</strong></span><br />\n另外參考連登既食評，由於良心經營既關係，黃店食物質素一般都偏高，<br />\n絕對係win win雙贏！<br />\n<br />\n------------國際文宣------------<br />\n請將買返黎既貨物/食物/單據同排隊盛況<br />\n一齊用<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#Buy4HK</span></span></strong><br />\n放上IG, Twitter, reddit"},{"pid":"b6559ced36a5559e2283561ea9e43939911fb1ff","tid":1634062,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c877b4b5ab4b0b8b8d3778e9a50b7beaa622b95","tid":1634062,"uid":279253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sorry記者朋友"},{"pid":"ea82f2b5bf9578d13e702f48232a7c235fff7c02","tid":1634062,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"